<%- include("./components/head.ejs") %>

<body>
    <%- include("./components/nav.ejs") %>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Weight Tracking</h1>
        <div class="cards-container">
            <div class="text-card">
                <p>
                    This website is designed to create an easy way to log your weight each day and tracking the changes week to week. Whether your goal is to gain or lose,
                    you will be able to track your progress easily.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-card">
                <p>
                    On the "Track" page, you can enter your weight for today as well as see the last seven days. If you need to delete the weight you most recently input, simply
                    click the trash icon next to the date.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-card">
                <p>On the "Previous" page, you can see how your weight has changed from week to week.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

